  "content": "### `IngestionAdapter`¥n### `TemporalStore`¥n¥n### `GraphStore`¥n¥nDirected knowledge graph interface. petgraph was chosen so that LiteStore gets full traversal¥ncapabilities (BFS, shortest path, cycle detection) without any external service. Supports edge¥ncreation, edge queries by direction, BFS traversal with optional relation filtering, and¥nshortest path computation.¥n¥n```rust¥npub trait GraphStore: Send + Sync {¥n    async fn relate(&self, from: &Uuid, relation: &str, to: &Uuid, metadata: Option<Value>) -> Result<()>;¥n    async fn edges(&self, entry_id: &Uuid, direction: EdgeDirection) -> Result<Vec<GraphEdge>>;¥n    async fn traverse(&self, start: &Uuid, relation: Option<&str>, direction: EdgeDirection, max_depth: usize) -> Result<Vec<KnowledgeEntry>>;¥n    async fn shortest_path(&self, from: &Uuid, to: &Uuid) -> Result<Option<Vec<KnowledgeEntry>>>;¥n    async fn remove_edges(&self, entry_id: &Uuid) -> Result<()>;¥n}¥n```¥n¥n**Implementations:** `LiteGraphStore` (petgraph DiGraph + Redb persistence).¥n",
